        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on FG’s article ["Hereditary improvement", <hi rend="italic">Fraser’s Mag.</hi> 87 (1873): 116–30]. Finds it "the sole feasible, yet I fear utopian, plan of procedure in improving the human race".</p> 
            <p>Thanks for rabbits for Balfour.</p> 
<p>Mentions reading W. R. Greg’s <hi rend="italic">Enigmas</hi> [<hi rend="italic">of life</hi> (1872)].</p> 
        </abstract>
